data.description: Well kept property in Washoe Valley with beautiful views of the surrounding mountains. Over an acre of land with room for horses and toys. Easy access to Washoe Lake. 1200 sqft garage converted to a huge bonus/game room with fireplace. Workshop and storage shed close to the home for easy access. New paint inside and out and many updates.  A spacious primary suite with large bathroom that includes double sinks, shower stall, and tub. Oversized deck to enjoy the views and back yard. Nice floor plan with separated primary bedroom from other bedrooms.
